The failure strength of a material at a given strain rate or after a given period under deviatoric stress. #{g: xqNSIDCCryosphere | h1635}

The failure strength of a material at a given strain rate or after a given period under deviatoric stress #{g: xqIPAPermafrost | h1630}

#{g: xqGCW | h1619}

Change in phase from ice directly into water vapour. #{g: xqWMOHydrology | h1642}

The transition of water from solid to gas without passing through the liquid phase. #{g: xqNOAA-NWS | h1633}

The change of phase of water from solid to gas without passing through the liquid phase. #{g: xqAMSglossary | h1620}

#{g: xqGCW | h1619}

A wedge showing evidence of both primary and secondary filling. #{g: xqNSIDCCryosphere | h1635}

A wedge showing evidence of both primary and secondary filling #{g: xqIPAPermafrost | h1630}

