The upper boundary surface of permafrost. #{g: xqNSIDCCryosphere | h1635}

The upper boundary surface of permafrost #{g: xqIPAPermafrost | h1630}

The upper boundary surface of Permafrost. #{g: xqTrombottoGeocryology | h1639}

(Also called pergelisol table.) The more or less irregular surface in the ground that marks the upper limit of the permafrost; not to be confused with frost table. #{g: xqAMSglossary | h1620}

