Ice that contains sediments stirred up and tangled in the ice as it grows. #{g: xqNSIDCCryosphere | h1635}

Ice that has a mineral or organic content of natural or anthropogenic origin on the surface or in its strata. #{g: xqBushuyev | h1623}

